data.description: Welcome home to 3407 Kirkwood Road! Located in the Academy Gardens section of Philadelphia. This home is ready for its new owners. You are greeted by the front covered porch where its perfect to sit and relax after a long day. Walking into the Living room there is tons of natural lighting, fresh paint, brand new blinds and seamless vinyl flooring that also runs into the Dining area. In the Dining Room there is also a fresh coat of paint, new light fixture and makes the perfect space for entertaining since it is just steps away from the kitchen. The eat in Kitchen features stainless steel appliances, solid wood cabinets with brand new hardware, and tile floors and backsplash. Right off of the kitchen is a conveniently located fully updated Half bathroom. Up stairs there are 3 bedrooms. All Bedrooms have new flooring, fresh paint, their own personal closet space, 6 panel doors, and new blinds. This level of the home is finished off with the hall bathroom that has a tub/shower combo, recessed lighting, and new vanity. In the finished basement there is the option to use this space as a 4th  bedroom or extra storage space. There is a separate entrance which allows for extra privacy and also a full bathroom on this level with a stall shower. The Laundry area can also be found on this level. The washer and dryer are included in the sale and are newer. Other notable features of this home are: Water heater 1 year old. Fully fenced yard. 1 Car driveway.  There is nothing to do here but unpack and enjoy your new home just in time for summer. Within Walking distance to parks, restaurants, shopping, and entertainment.
